{"tid":1892272,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友話要睇塔羅先決定同唔同我繼續落去","createTime":"2020-02-22T11:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T20:16:48.000Z","uid":317241,"like":1,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bb48263ebb6b38672aa631f00c43cf3ce3841c5e","tid":1892272,"uid":317241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:55:56.000Z","msg":"同ex 11月分左手<br />\n知道佢分左手之後就上網識男仔<br />\n就算仲好鐘意佢 本身都好絕望 諗住算<br />\n唔再煩佢 唯有遠遠咁祝福佢<br />\n<br />\n1月尾 佢搵返我 聯絡返<br />\n宜家算係一齊返咁 會做情侶做既野<br />\n但佢就點都唔肯做返我女朋友 話佢4月前唔會拍拖<br />\n<br />\n我問點解要咁堅持4月<br />\n佢話塔羅師叫佢4月前都唔好拍拖 叫佢唔好害人 話4月後先有轉機<br />\n不過就叫佢識啲新朋友 （所以佢先玩網上交友app)<br />\n但其實講真 邊有人玩交友app真係純粹為咗識朋友...<br />\n<br />\n我問4月之後點 佢話再去睇塔羅<br />\n先決定同唔同返我一齊<br />\n<br />\n我聽完好嬲 又無奈 唔明點解要由塔羅決定自己既未來...<br />\n<br />\n如果各位巴絲係我 會點做？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：繼續堅持打動佢，同時希望塔羅勸佢同返我一齊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：爆佢，佢唔珍惜就算，拎返自己既尊嚴"},{"pid":"a9aa58c9e4d1e99ac0459b9f5acd4547ab4bd12a","tid":1892272,"uid":258683,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:59:25.000Z","msg":"屌 條女都on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁嘅野都講得出口<br />\n仲要玩埋交友app<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哩啲女好行夾唔送啦"},{"pid":"a95b594e8f9c5c0e95a250119376038d4be5fc0a","tid":1892272,"uid":78429,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:32:28.000Z","msg":"塔羅師有冇話每個禮拜要屌幾多次先可以轉運"},{"pid":"bfc734b0175fa7099afccffe1b8afc33bf4f86fd","tid":1892272,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T14:47:42.000Z","msg":"塔乜鳩羅 神神化化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2da3b48ddab83f020546000f963cd8193bb61f","tid":1892272,"uid":66547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T14:49:11.000Z","msg":"用巨龍睡服她吧！"},{"pid":"842bd6d057cad060e82c9b6ec09daaea883b2fee","tid":1892272,"uid":310812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:08:52.000Z","msg":"信副牌都唔信你 手足自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9ae41426e2274a49080dfaa79d2d276b0c4739","tid":1892272,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:25:30.000Z","msg":"jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d8e5ddd511865dd1cbdb4812a16642ba56ec88","tid":1892272,"uid":118286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:31:32.000Z","msg":"咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a84a4acd459df43b3c38b387809a633e1b0f281","tid":1892272,"uid":317241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9aa58c9e4d1e99ac0459b9f5acd4547ab4bd12a","tid":1892272,"uid":258683,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:59:25.000Z","msg":"屌 條女都on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁嘅野都講得出口<br />\n仲要玩埋交友app<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哩啲女好行夾唔送啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:41:12.000Z","msg":"但係我真係好鐘意佢 所以唔知應該點<br />\n仲有一個幾月就到4月<br />\n好驚到時個塔羅師叫佢離開我 搵第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00651afcd6de6e813f4ee4c919ad7bab97843181","tid":1892272,"uid":317241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"842bd6d057cad060e82c9b6ec09daaea883b2fee","tid":1892272,"uid":310812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:08:52.000Z","msg":"信副牌都唔信你 手足自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:44:33.000Z","msg":"我都想同佢講命運終究都係掌握係自己手上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋分手個2個月 我好努力做左好多改變<br />\n佢見返我都有感受到我變好左<br />\n<br />\n只係一諗起佢4月要去塔羅決定一唔一齊<br />\n真心好不安<br />\n但係我唔知點樣先說服到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582022e8d624f11427a027a86385feddc68af3f3","tid":1892272,"uid":265403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T13:18:23.000Z","msg":"係咪本身識咗另一個<br />\n之後對方話4月先答佢一唔一齊<br />\n所以佢到時先答到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有等下啦"},{"pid":"c809e24a08e9beef9aa5bfa57eb0a57c9af81c28","tid":1892272,"uid":317241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"582022e8d624f11427a027a86385feddc68af3f3","tid":1892272,"uid":265403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T13:18:23.000Z","msg":"係咪本身識咗另一個<br />\n之後對方話4月先答佢一唔一齊<br />\n所以佢到時先答到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有等下啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔想咁 好無安全感"},{"pid":"95068d3c2ed9bd363212bab6be13c3a6b6ac203f","tid":1892272,"uid":58702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T20:16:48.000Z","msg":"手足依家點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}